{"id":"summaries/2021-07-29-love-your-parents-so-you-free-yourself-from-the-hate","title":"Love your parents, so you free yourself from the hate","type":"summaries","html":"<p>July 2021 <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">Yahir</a> one-line family-philosophy aphorism: <em>\"Love your parents, so you free yourself from the hate. If you hate, you'll damage yourself.\"</em> Connects the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/mom-yahir\">mom</a> and <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/dad-yahir\">dad</a> threads with the broader self-discipline philosophy that recurs in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/voluntary-adversity\">voluntary adversity</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">yahir gonzalez</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/mom-yahir\">mom yahir</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/dad-yahir\">dad yahir</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/voluntary-adversity\">voluntary adversity</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"entities/dad-yahir","label":"Dad Yahir"},{"id":"entities/mom-yahir","label":"Mom (Yahir's mother)"},{"id":"concepts/voluntary-adversity","label":"Voluntary Adversity"},{"id":"entities/yahir-gonzalez","label":"Yahir Gonzalez"}]}
